    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no scratches, dents, or chips whatsoever. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, smelling like new with absolutely no wear on the leather seats or carpets. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been kept in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at the dealership. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model.",
